<manpage>
    <sample url="system_lib\EzFlushInstructionCache"> CProcess::FlushInstructionCache</sample>
    <volume>进程</volume>
    <title>CProcess::FlushInstructionCache</title>
    <routine_idx>../../../Process.htm</routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>刷出当前进程所对应的指令缓存。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>ECode</return_val>
        <parameters>
            <api_param>
                <param_type> PVoid </param_type>
                <param_name> baseAddr </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[in]需要刷新的cache块的基址 </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_type> MemorySize </param_type>
                <param_name> size </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[in]需要刷新的cache块的大小</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
    	<table>
            <th>
                <td>返回值</td><td>描述</td>
            </th>
            <tr>
                <td>NOERROR</td><td>程序执行成功</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>E_INVALID_ARGUMENT</td><td>所要刷新的Cache块超出了进程空间的地址范围</td>
            </tr>

        </table>
        <para>参见<link url="../../../../../../car_technology/fundamental/development_environment/car/ECode.htm">ECode</link>相关帮助。</para>
    </return>

    <remarks>
    	<para>如果用户修改了内存中的代码，而cpu不能检测到此改动，则有可能去执行缓存中老的代码。此时就需要调用<link url="../../../../../../SoftwareDevelopmentManual/CoreServices/ProcessThread/ProcessThread/Function/CProcess/FlushInstructionCache.htm">CProcess::FlushInstructionCache</link>用以将数据缓存中的代码部分刷出到内存中，并强制使指令缓存中相应的部分失效，使其必须重新去读内存。此方法只能用于当前进程上下文中。</para>

    </remarks>

    <requirements>
        <system>
            <system_name>
                Windows 2000 或更高版本；Elastos操作系统 
            </system_name>
        </system>
        <headerfile>
            <file_name> elastos.h </file_name>
        </headerfile>
        <library>
            <lib_name> elastos.lib </lib_name>
        </library>
    </requirements>

